text: Sekolah Menengah Kebangsaan Taman Daya (or TDS (Taman Daya School) is a secondary school located in Jalan Rumbia 39, Taman Daya, Johor Bahru, Johor, Malaysia. ==See also== * Education in Malaysia Category:1995 establishments in Malaysia Category:Educational institutions established in 1995 Category:Johor Bahru Category:Secondary schools in Malaysia Category:Schools in Johor
